{"tha-ap468:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap468:0.2":"Salakusumiyavagga ","tha-ap468:0.3":"6 Avataphaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap468:1.1":"“Sataramsi nama bhagava, ","tha-ap468:1.2":"sayambhu aparajito; ","tha-ap468:1.3":"Vivekakamo sambuddho, ","tha-ap468:1.4":"gocarayabhinikkhami. ","tha-ap468:2.1":"Phalahattho aham disva, ","tha-ap468:2.2":"upagacchim narasabham; ","tha-ap468:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap468:2.4":"adasim avatam phalam. ","tha-ap468:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap468:3.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap468:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap468:3.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap468:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap468:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap468:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap468:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap468:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap468:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap468:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap468:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap468:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap468:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma avataphaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap468:8.1":"Avataphaliyattherassapadanam chattham. "}